title: Planned Parenthood Supporters Will Hand-Deliver 80,000 Petitions to Paul Ryan’s Office Today
text: After yesterday’s news confirming that the GOP is planning to strip Planned Parenthood of its funding as a part of their bill to repeal the Affordable Care Act, Planned Parenthood supporters began flooding Paul Ryan’s office with phone calls protesting the decision.
